high_descs: Turn left, walk forward until wall, turn left towards the side of the dining table.
Take the tomato from the dining table.
Turn left, right towards the front side of the dining table, look at the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the tomato inside, close it, turn on, wait, turn off, open the microwave, get back the tomato, close the microwave.
Turn right, move, turn left, towards the side of the dining table.
Put the tomato on the corner of the dining table.
anns.task_desc: To heat the tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left and walk straight to reach the side of the dining table on which microwave oven is placed
Take the tomato from the dining table
Turn left and come in front of the microwave oven
Open the oven and put the tomato into the oven and close it. After few seconds, open the door and take the tomato out and again close the oven.
Turn right and take immediate left to reach the side of the dining table again
Put the tomato on the dining table
anns.task_desc: Put the tomato on the dining table

high_descs: Go straight to the dining table
Pick the tomato from the  dining table
Put the tomato into the oven heat it and take it back
Turn around and walk back to the dining table
Place the tomato on the dining table
anns.task_desc: Place the tomato on the dining table
